com.manofwar.logic

Class GameStateManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.manofwar.logic.GameStateManager

  • public class GameStateManager
extends java.lang.Object
    GameStateManager is to control the game state and contains all its game objects. Manages coherence between utility managers and game objects. Contains all managers and game objects but interferes with them as little as possible.
